lead_paragraph: Stephen Larkham will stand down as coach of the ACT Brumbies at the end of the next Super Rugby season to take up a full-time position in the Wallabies set-up, the Australian Rugby Union said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Larkham to Leave Brumbies for Permanent Wallabies Role
headline.main: Larkham to Leave Brumbies for Permanent Wallabies Role
